            "block_1_eyebrow": "THE ASSIGNMENT: CANNES",
            "block_1_headline": "A Decade of Opening Doors for the Next Generation.",
            "block_1_body": "<p>True stewardship isn't just about walking the carpet; it's about building a gateway for the next generation to step into their own original design. For years, the House has used the world's most prestigious stages as a platform to mentor young visionaries—cloaking them in the dignity of couture and the reality of their high calling.</p>",
