    "ktvu_press_feature": {
      "type": "ktvu-feature",
      "settings": {
        "eyebrow": "LATEST BROADCAST",
        "heading": "LEADING WITH GLOBAL IMPACT",
        "sub_headline": "Refining the Narrative of Success through Bespoke Excellence",
        "body_copy": "Nancy Vuu joins KTVU Fox 2 for a standing interview to discuss the architecture of identity and her mission to restore purpose through couture. The segment spotlights her specialized work in bridal gowns and the expansion of Seth Eden suits, exploring how high-fashion serves as a medium for restorative leadership. Recognized as a global voice of influence, Nancy shares how her entry into the industry was a calling to integrate world-class craftsmanship with strategic initiatives designed to inspire and elevate.",
        "pull_quote": "Beyond the runway, Nancy Vuu is building something deeper—guiding global leaders with faith-driven strategy, and expanding her influence through fashion, film, and community-focused initiatives designed to inspire, empower, and elevate.\"",
